.row.content-header
  .col-md-12.col-sm-12
    h1 WHAT MAKES CODESMITH UNIQUE?
  
.row.codesmith-values.top.content-row
  .col-md-4.col-sm-12
    h3 BRILLIANT TEACHERS
    p 
      | Our curriculum team literally created some of the frameworks you'll use as software engineers every day 
      a href="http://www.mongodb.com/profile/nuri-halperin" Nuri (Mongodb)
      | , 
      a href="http://icecomm.io" Will & Alex (Icecomm)
      | . They've run engineering teams that serve millions of users and have accumulated 10,000 hours of teaching between them.
  .col-md-4.col-sm-12
    h3 FULLSTACK EDUCATION
    p 
      |We teach computer science and full stack development in JavaScript - the language of the modern web 
      a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zXqs6X0lzKI"
      |. You'll learn NodeJS/Express on the backend and ReactJS and AngularJS on the frontend.
  .col-md-4.col-sm-12
    h3 LEARN THROUGH BUILDING
    p 
      | We help you   
      em build to learn 
      | not just 
      em learn to code
      | . Working in pairs you’ll face challenging projects where you’ll need to hunt out the answer (with the total support of our Engineers In Residence - 1 for every 4 students). Lectures provide an incredible baseline and are taught by masters in their fields

.row.codesmith-values.bottom.content-row
  .col-md-4.col-sm-12.image-panel
  .col-md-4.col-sm-12
    h3 COMMUNITY FOR LIFE
    p 
      | Attending Codesmith is a focused engineering experience but it's also about welcoming you into a community of creative and technical people who become lifelong allies. 
      br
      | Every graduate has life-time access to our co-working space at our LA HQ (it even has a bar).
  .col-md-4.col-sm-12
    h3 MOBILE DEVELOPMENT
    p 
      | Learn the fundamentals of mobile development - hardware performance, networking and native features
      br
      | With Facebook's transformative new framework ReactJS, you'll also be the first students in the world to build full-powered 
      a href="http://www.webdesignerdepot.com/2015/03/facebookss-react-native-radically-simplifies-app-development/" mobile apps with JavaScript. 
  

