    h2 8 WEEK SUMMER PROGRAM
  .col-md-12.col-sm-12
    p The 8 week Summer program is designed for determined college students who want to build incredible production-level apps, graduate with the tools and portfolio of projects to land the very best roles in tech, or even launch their own ventures.
    p 
      | You'll be part of the most extraordinary class you'll ever take - a group of CS majors, MBAs, and Biochemical Engineers all learning modern software engineering.
    p
