.row.our-programs.accelerator.non-top.content-row
  .col-md-12.col-sm-12.codesmith-college
    h2 4 Week Coding Accelerator (Evenings and Weekends)
  .col-md-12.col-sm-12
    .summary 
      p Beginner level course: The Fundamentals of Front-end web development. The Codesmith Software Engineering Accelerator takes you from an <span class="underline">initial curiosity with coding</span> to the <span class="underline">ability to build full apps</span>
    p You'll be introduced to the unique Codesmith approach of Learning by Building. There's no better way to accelerate your coding abilities
    ol
      li Concept Lectures - We give you a conceptual model of core programming concepts and connect it to code
      li Learn programming by programming - You will build projects and complete challenges to help you develop as a coder for life, not just 4 weeks
      li Engineers in Residence - You'll have the total support of our Engineers in Residence (EIRs). When you hit a learning block, you can expect support with your coding in under 5 minutes
  .col-md-6.col-sm-12
    p You'll learn software engineering fundamentals by building projects, not by watching tutorials. You'll build projects including:
    ul
      li A YouTube app
      li An anonymous video chat app
      li Snake and Pacman games
      li A mobile optimized version of Instagram
    p You have:
    ul
      li a desire to experiment and build things (maybe you loved lego as a kid - or still do)
      li a curiosity with coding and web development
      li the need to direct your own career path
  .col-md-6.col-sm-12
    
.row.our-programs.non-top.content-row  
  .col-md-3.col-sm-12
    h3 Software engineering fundamentals
    p Learn the fundamentals of programming in JavaScript. We'll cover variables, operators, functions, Objects, arrrays, loops, conditionals and even callbacks and higher order functions - all the skills and techniques to program effectively
  .col-md-3.col-sm-12
    h3 JavaScript for building websites and apps
    p By building apps you'll learn how to create and change elements on the page using basic JavaScript and jQuery. You'll get live data from a server API and even add video chat to  your site
  .col-md-3.col-sm-12
    h3 HTML5 and CSS3
    p Transform your site with HTML5 video, canvas elements as well as HTML fundamentals including tags, links, layout. Learn to build responsive sites using CSS3 including selectors, classes and media queries. Add animations with CSS3 animations
  .col-md-3.col-sm-12
    h3 Software engineer tools
    p Learn how to use Git, Github and the core tools used by software engineers to 'deploy' your applications online
.row.our-programs.non-top.content-row
