.row.our-students.content-row
  .col-md-3.col-sm-12
    h3 DETERMINED AND AMBITIOUS
    p You're ready to focus completely on learning to code and prepared to work with your cohort to achieve things you never thought possible before you started the program.
  .col-md-3.col-sm-12
    h3 GREAT PEOPLE
    p We're building a community of good people who will become empathetic engineers. You get a kick out of the idea of pair programming - working with other students to learn faster than you ever could alone.
  .col-md-3.col-sm-12
    h3 LOVE LEARNING
    p Nothing excites you more than the thought of how many new things you'll come to understand over the 8 weeks program and following academic year with Codesmith.
  .col-md-3.col-sm-12
    h3 BUILDERS
